        "query": "Using the supplied transcripts and celebration frames only, determine which answer option is supported. First quote the transcript phrases that show the coach's team won rather than lost, tied, cancelled, or disqualified. Then inspect the celebration frames and identify the jersey color of the celebrating trophy-winning team. Finally map to exactly one option among: A cancelled, B black team won, C white team won, D tied, E disqualified.",
